9\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What you need to know:  He has the pedigree.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only was he supposed to be the GM for the Beijing team before the NHL withdrew, but the 53-year-old represented the United States in the Olympics three times as a player (1998 in Nagano, 2002 in Salt Lake City and 2006 in Torino), winning a silver medal in 2002.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.727700005603325e-23, \"text\": \"GM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Guoan_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beijing team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Guoan_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Guoan_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.472470703682956e-28, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}, {\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.023010236298406e-26, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1998_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.501477370626166e-24, \"text\": \"Nagano\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1998_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1998_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998995008, \"rank\": 1.0039198713709402e-10, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7055465332695657e-15, \"text\": \"Torino\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_Winter_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  Guerin played 18 years in the NHL, winning two Stanley Cups as a player, with theNew Jersey Devilsin 1995 andPittsburgh Penguinsin 2009; two more as a Penguins executive (2016 and 2017); and he was inducted into the U.S. Hockey Hall of Fame in 2013.\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.472470703682956e-28, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is tied for the eighth-most goals (429) amongst U.S.-born players in NHL history.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.472470703682956e-28, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just super excited for this opportunity,\\\" Guerin toldThe Athleticon Thursday.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was 9 years old when the Miracle on Ice happened, and that was very impactful in my life and my love for hockey and my desire to represent my country.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So this means a lot.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It really does.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I take it very seriously.\\\"\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin has been the Wild GM since 2019, during which time the team is 191-113-35 and has not missed the playoffs, though they also have not advanced to the second round.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652373322912568e-32, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Minnesota is currently in seventh place in the Central Division at 22-23-5.- Michael Russo, senior NHL writer  While Canada is the usual favorite, Guerin's Team USA will be stacked, arguably possessing the best roster on paper.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_ice_hockey\", \"score\": 0.9992809827992681, \"rank\": 0.0007193551313515146, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_ice_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_ice_hockey\"}, {\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League_Central\", \"score\": 0.9566730652397403, \"rank\": 0.04523338678224128, \"text\": \"Central Division\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League_Central\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League_Central\"}, {\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Russo_(rugby_league)\", \"score\": 0.9999601864237343, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Russo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Russo_(rugby_league)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Russo_(rugby_league)\"}, {\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.472470703682956e-28, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2704201229249864e-13, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652373322912568e-32, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}, {\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso