\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And any of their top three goalies could start for Canada, which lacks depth there.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1785, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2704201229249864e-13, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it's the 4 Nations Cup or the Olympics, the Americans will be in prime position internationally with this generation of NHLers.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Guerin said his dream is to manage the U.S. to gold medals in both: \\\"That's the goal.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1956, \"end\": 1962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652373322912568e-32, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"USA Hockey has come so far in the last 25 years that it's no longer good enough to just participate.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2042, \"end\": 2052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Hockey\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We go in with the expectation of winning, and that's what I love.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have skilled centers.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have shutdown (defensemen).\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have 100-point guys.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have good role players.\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is so much to choose from.\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just do not see why we should not be thinking gold medals.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Russo and Joe Smith, senior Wild writer  Advertisement  It's hard to imagine a Team USA withoutDetroit Red WingswingerPatrick Kane, arguably the greatest American-born player of all time.\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2424, \"end\": 2427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9927938760121585, \"rank\": 0.007221987762422494, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 2493, \"end\": 2501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.228412406678138e-21, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But to select him or not will be among the harder decisions Guerin has to make, as will another veteran and international constant,Dallas StarsforwardJoe Pavelski.\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.652373322912568e-32, \"text\": \"Guerin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Guerin\", \"